<BIG><B>八連荘</B></BIG>
<BIG><B>8 consecutive win</B></BIG>
<BR>
以下の定義に従って親の連荘が役満になる。
According to the following definitions, the dealers's win becomes Yakuman.
<BR>
但し、操作設定で、"アプリで点数計算"がOFFの場合と、
"一翻縛り"の"チェックする"がOFFの場合は八連荘は無効になる。
However, in the operation settings, if "Evaluate Point" is OFF,
or if "Check 1-han constraint" is OFF, "8 consecutive win" will be disabled.
標準役でないローカル役の場合も考慮されないので"和了申告"ダイアログで設定してください。
Local Yaku that are not standard Yaku are not taken into consideration, so please set them in the "Win Claim" dialog.
"流し満貫"を"和了扱い"としても連続和了数はリセットされ八連荘の和了ともなりません。
Even if setting of "NagashiMangan" is "Win", the number of consecutive winnings will be reset and it will not be a winning of "8 consecutive win".
<BR>
親マークのそばにそのプレーヤーの連続和了数が表示されています。
The number of consecutive wins for that player is displayed near the parent mark.
<BR>
<B>親で連続和了の８回目</B>："連続和了数＞積み棒本数" のとき和了数には直前の子としての上がりが含まれる。
<B>8 times as dealer</B>: When "Number of consecutive wins > Number of piled sticks", the number of wins includes the win as the immediately preceding non-dealer.
"連続和了数＜積み棒本数" のとき積み棒に親流れの流局数が含まれる。
When "Number of consecutive wins < Number of piles sticks", the number of sticks include the count of drawn.
このオプションは、小さいほうが７の時の親の和了を八連荘の役満とする。
This option makes the dealer's win as Yakuman of "8 consecutive win" when the smaller one is 7.
<BR>
<B>親で連続和了の９回目</B>：連続和了数と積み棒本数の小さいほうが８の時親の和了を八連荘の役満とする。
<B>9 times as dealer</B>: When the Number of consecutive wins and the Number of piled sticks, whichever is smaller, is 8, the parent's win will be considered as Yarkuman.
<BR>
<B>子からでも８連続</B>：連続和了数が 7 の時の親の和了を八連荘の役満とする。
<B>Start may be non-dealer</B>: When the number of consecutive wins is 7, the parent's win is considered as Yakuman.
<BR>
<B>８本場で親の和了</B>：流局の積み棒が何本含まれていてもＯＫ。分かりやすい。
<B>Dealer's win when 8 sticks</B>: Any number of stickes by Drawn-round can be included. Easy to understand.
<BR>
<B>次は＋８</B>：OFFなら子が上がるか流局するまでまで親の上りはすべて役満。
<B>Next is +8</B>: If it's OFF, all dealer's win is Yakuman until the non-dealer's win or Drawn-round.
ONなら次の８連続目で役満。
If it is ON, the next 8 consecutive is the next Yakuman timing.
<BR>
-------------------------------------------------------
<BIG><B>八連荘</B></BIG>
<BR>
以下の定義に従って親の連荘が役満になる。
<BR>
但し、操作設定で、"アプリで点数計算"がOFFの場合と、
"一翻縛り"の"チェックする"がOFFの場合は八連荘は無効になる。
標準役でないローカル役の場合も考慮されないので"和了申告"ダイアログで設定してください。
"流し満貫"を"和了扱い"としても連続和了数はリセットされ八連荘の和了ともなりません。
<BR>
親マークのそばにそのプレーヤーの連続和了数が表示されています。
<BR>
<B>親で連続和了の８回目</B>："連続和了数＞積み棒本数" のとき和了数には直前の子としての上がりが含まれる。
"連続和了数＜積み棒本数" のとき積み棒に親流れの流局数が含まれる。
このオプションは、小さいほうが７の時の親の和了を八連荘の役満とする。
<BR>
<B>親で連続和了の９回目</B>：連続和了数と積み棒本数の小さいほうが８の時親の和了を八連荘の役満とする。
<BR>
<B>子からでも８連続</B>：連続和了数が 7 の時の親の和了を八連荘の役満とする。
<BR>
<B>８本場で親の和了</B>：流局の積み棒が何本含まれていてもＯＫ。分かりやすい。
<BR>
<B>次は＋８</B>：OFFなら子が上がるか流局するまでまで親の上りはすべて役満。
ONなら次の８連続目で役満。
<BR>
-------------------------------------------------------
<BIG><B>8 consecutive win</B></BIG>
<BR>
According to the following definitions, the dealers's win becomes Yakuman.
<BR>
However, in the operation settings, if "Evaluate Point" is OFF,
or if "Check 1-han constraint" is OFF, "8 consecutive win" will be disabled.
Local Yaku that are not standard winning pattern are not taken into consideration, so please set Yakuman in the "Win Claim" dialog.
Even if setting of "NagashiMangan" is "Win", "NagashiMangan" resets the number of consecutive win and it will not be a winning of "8 consecutive win".
<BR>
The number of consecutive wins for the player is displayed near the Dealer-Mark.
<BR>
<B>8 times as dealer</B>: When "Number of consecutive wins > Number of piled sticks", the number of wins includes the win as the immediately preceding non-dealer.
When "Number of consecutive wins < Number of piles sticks", the number of sticks include the count of Drawn-round.
This option makes the dealer's win as Yakuman of "8 consecutive win" when the smaller one is 7.
<BR>
<B>9 times as dealer</B>: When the Number of consecutive wins and the Number of piled sticks, whichever is smaller, is 8, the dealer's win will be considered as Yarkuman.
<BR>
<B>Start may be non-dealer</B>: When the number of consecutive wins is 7, the dealer's win is considered as Yakuman.
<BR>
<B>Dealer's win when 8 sticks</B>: Any number of stickes by Drawn-round can be included. This option is easy to judge.
<BR>
<B>Next is +8</B>: If this is OFF, all dealer's win is Yakuman until the non-dealer's win or Drawn-round.
If this is ON, the next 8 consecutive is the next Yakuman timing.
<BR>
-------------------------------------------------------
<BIG><B>8 consecutive win</B></BIG>
<BR>
According to the following definitions, the dealers's _win becomes Yakuman.
다음 정의에 따르면 딜러의 win은 Yakuman이 됩니다.
<BR>
However, in the operation settings, if "Evaluate Point" is OFF,
or if "Check 1-han constraint" is OFF, "8 _consecutive _win" will be disabled.
단, 동작 설정에서 "Evaluate Point"가 OFF인 경우,
또는 "1-han 제약 확인"이 OFF인 경우 "8 consecutive win"이 비활성화됩니다.
"Local Yaku" which is not a standard winning pattern may not be a valid win. So please set _Yakuman in the "_Win _Claim" dialog.
표준 승리 패턴이 아닌 "Local Yaku"는 유효한 승리가 아닐 수 있습니다. 따라서 "Win Claim" 대화 상자에서 _Yakuman을 설정하십시오.
Even if setting of "_NagashiMangan" is "_Win", "_NagashiMangan" resets the "_Number _of _consecutive _win" and it will not be a winning of "8 _consecutive _win".
"NagashiMangan"의 설정이 "Win"인 경우에도 "NagashiMangan"은 "Number of conecutive win"을 재설정하고 "8 conecutive win"의 승리가 아닙니다.
<BR>
The "_number_of_consecutive_wins" for each is displayed near the Dealer-Mark.
각각의 "Number of consecutive wins"는 딜러 마크 근처에 표시됩니다.
<BR>
<B>8_times_as_dealer</B>: When "Number_of_consecutive_wins > Number_of_piled_sticks", the number of wins includes the win as the immediately preceding non-dealer.
<B>8 times as dealer</B>: "Number of consecutive wins > Number of piled sticks"인 경우, 승리 횟수에는 바로 앞의 논딜러로서의 승리도 포함됩니다.
When "Number_of_consecutive_wins < Number_of_piles_sticks", the number of sticks include the count of Drawn-round(流局).
"Number of consecutive wins < Number of piles sticks"일 때, 스틱의 수는 무승부(流局)의 카운트를 포함합니다.
This option makes the dealer's win as Yakuman of "8_consecutive_win" when the smaller one is 7.
이 옵션은 작은 것이 7일 때 "8 consecutive win"의 Yakuman으로 딜러의 승리를 만듭니다.
<BR>
<B>9_times_as_dealer</B>: When the Number_of_consecutive_wins and the Number_of_piled_sticks, whichever is smaller, is 8, the dealer's win will be considered as Yarkuman.
<B>9 times as dealer</B>: Number of consecutive wins 및 Number of piled sticks 중 작은 쪽이 8일 때 딜러의 승리는 Yarkuman으로 간주됩니다.
<BR>
<B>Start_may_be_non-dealer</B>: When Number_of_consecutive_wins is 7, the dealer's win is considered as Yakuman.
<B>Start may be non dealer</B>: Number of consecutive wins가 7일 때 딜러의 승리는 Yakuman으로 간주됩니다.
<BR>
<B>Dealer's_win_when_8_sticks</B>: Number of stickes may contains count of _Drawn_round. This option is easy to judge.
<B>Dealer's win when 8 sticks</B>: 스틱 수에는 Drawn-round의 수가 포함될 수 있습니다. 이 옵션은 판단하기 쉽습니다.
<BR>
<B>Next is +8</B>: If this is OFF, the dealer's win is all Yakuman until the _non-dealer's_win or _Drawn-round.
<B>Next is +8</B>: 이것이 OFF이면 딜러의 승리는 non-dealer's win 또는 Drawn-round까지 모두 Yakuman입니다.
If this is ON, the next 8 consecutive is the next Yakuman timing.
ON이면 다음 8연속이 다음 야쿠만 타이밍입니다.
<BR>
-------------------------------------------------------
<BIG><B>8 consecutive win</B></BIG>
<BR>
다음 정의에 따르면 딜러의 win은 Yakuman이 됩니다.
<BR>
단, 동작 설정에서 "Evaluate Point"가 OFF인 경우,
또는 "1-han 제약 확인"이 OFF인 경우 "8 consecutive win"이 비활성화됩니다.
표준 승리 패턴이 아닌 "Local Yaku"는 유효한 승리가 아닐 수 있습니다. 따라서 "Win Claim" 대화 상자에서 _Yakuman을 설정하십시오.
"NagashiMangan"의 설정이 "Win"인 경우에도 "NagashiMangan"은 "Number of conecutive win"을 재설정하고 "8 conecutive win"의 승리가 아닙니다.
<BR>
각각의 "Number of consecutive wins"는 딜러 마크 근처에 표시됩니다.
<BR>
<B>8 times as dealer</B>: "Number of consecutive wins > Number of piled sticks"인 경우, 승리 횟수에는 바로 앞의 논딜러로서의 승리도 포함됩니다.
"Number of consecutive wins < Number of piles sticks"일 때, 스틱의 수는 무승부(流局)의 카운트를 포함합니다.
이 옵션은 작은 것이 7일 때 "8 consecutive win"의 Yakuman으로 딜러의 승리를 만듭니다.
<BR>
<B>9 times as dealer</B>: Number of consecutive wins 및 Number of piled sticks 중 작은 쪽이 8일 때 딜러의 승리는 Yarkuman으로 간주됩니다.
<BR>
<B>Start may be non dealer</B>: Number of consecutive wins가 7일 때 딜러의 승리는 Yakuman으로 간주됩니다.
<BR>
<B>Dealer's win when 8 sticks</B>: 스틱 수에는 Drawn-round의 수가 포함될 수 있습니다. 이 옵션은 판단하기 쉽습니다.
<BR>
<B>Next is +8</B>: 이것이 OFF이면 딜러의 승리는 non-dealer's win 또는 Drawn-round까지 모두 Yakuman입니다.
ON이면 다음 8연속이 다음 야쿠만 타이밍입니다.
<BR>
